Description: Skin is often exposed to the harmful rays of the sun, pollution and other foreign bodies. A regular massage will not only help rejuvenate your skin but also prepares your skin to face dust, dirt, wrinkles and other signs of ageing on a regular basis. So make your skin look vibrant and youthful with this massage cream from Vaadi. It is suitable for all skin types.  Reduces Premature Skin Ageing This massage cream is enriched with lavender oil, rosemary oil, almond oil, mulethi extract, and carrot seed oil. Lavender and rosemary oils are effective as anti-ageing agents. Lavender oil even tones your skin and helps in the removal of sun tan. Rosemary oil is therapeutic in nature, so it penetrates into the deep layers of your skin and helps improve blood circulation. Almond oil provides moisture to your skin, making it healthier, smoother and glowing. Wrinkles and premature skin aging are treated effectively with carrot oil.

Title: Living Proof Cell Recovery Night Hydration Complex(30 ml)
Description: Clear facial skin is a sign of health and a beauty addition to the overall look. And nighttime moisturizing is a necessity to wake up with soft skin in the morning. Knowing this, Living Proof has brought out its Cell Recovery Night Hydration Complex. The cream, which comes in a bottle for easy use, can be used by both men and women to obtain hydrated facial skin. The Night Hydration Complex cream works on all skin types, making it suitable for the use of everybody. The cell recovery cream is made from completely natural elements such as olive oil, glycerin, soy protein and sweet almond oil. These contents work on facial skin, oxidising it and making it softer through the night. They lighten the skin and the cell recovering properties of the organic cream renews the skin, making it fresh from within. Applied during the night, the cream provides strength and elasticity to facial skin. So you can wake up to soft, healthy skin in the morning. Directions for use Apply a small amount of Cell Recovery Night Hydration Complex cream to face and neck. Massage with light circular motions until the cream is absorbed. Wash application area before use. Use every night for best results.
